data.description: IMPROVED PRICE !! This local chef and his designer wife create luxury living in every home they own. With less than 1000characters I will attempt to describe this amazing property: Through the gated entrance and up the winding road, this beauty sits high on 8ac, overlooking miles of country wildlife and the most beautiful sunsets in Oklahoma. Heavy double arched doors welcome you into the impressive entry. Selected appointments include: 4 large bedrooms, gorgeous study, 2 dining rooms, chef kitchen with large walk-in pantry, resort style living room with floor to ceiling wood burning fireplace, wine room, upstairs theatre room with dry kitchen, spa, outdoor kitchen with FP, upgraded water filtration system throughout, RV install, generator and high end lighting are just a few. Click on supplements for full list. A beautiful country setting so close to the city. Only 15 miles north of Kilpatrick of Rockwell exit.
